Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:35.94,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Liquor and Gasoline, Smiles and Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:41.95,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You people throw the word \Nbrother around too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:47.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Gin-san nor I am interested \Nin being brothers, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:48.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpa—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.97,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you come here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:00.47,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,when it's already too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.27,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.05,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.45,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yamazaki-san told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That you guys were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:31.01,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That he wouldn't be returning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who went and decided that it was over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.50,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:43.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That guy will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:48.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll bring him back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:53.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So can you wait just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Please. I promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:19.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.68,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:27.56,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So Gin-san, don't disappear on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.35,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Hajime-nii returns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.93,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and Earth is saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.19,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be smiling if \Nyou're not with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.86,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you don't \Nact like a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you're the total \Nopposite of a role model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.77,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you aren't \Nshowing us the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're with us \Nwhen we've lost our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:57.61,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're by our side, \Nsharing the pain and sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:02.02,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,As long as everybody's by \Nour side, we'll be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.78,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how difficult it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So can you let us take it from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.52,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.80,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer the crybaby \Nlittle brother of Obi Hajime,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.52,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,nor am I a student of the \NSchool of Beam Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I am the successor of the \NSchool of Tendo Mushin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.69,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and Odd Jobs' Shimura Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Shin—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.45,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.93,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Gin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:30.77,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.97,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Gin-san for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me tell you to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.14,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:58.27,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You want to fight a man who completely \Ndestroyed your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.91,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.58,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san didn't come here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He came to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.21,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If Gin-san had come to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.03,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't be standing \Nbefore me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.54,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get Hajime-nii back \Neven if I have to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:20.07,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how much \Npain it may cause me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:24.37,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,If you go through life with the blood \Nof your benefactor on your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.47,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be the only one \Nwho suffers as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:34.21,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I, Shimura Tae, will be the \Nwitness for this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:37.18,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The School of Tendo Mushin \Nand the School of Beam Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.82,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,in a no-holds-barred duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.05,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Fight as true warriors to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.82,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Boss lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.17,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch us, Obi-one-niisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:51.59,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The crybaby who always \Nfollowed you around
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.89,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,and all of us who always \Nadmired your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.23,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,have become much stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.53,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,after meeting you and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.27,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Strong enough to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:07.90,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Begin now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:19.10,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.36,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Shin-bo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:55.35,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen the future of \Nthe School of Tendo Mushin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:02.35,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You've become so strong, \NShin-bo, Otae-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:22.67,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.76,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost contact with Kenofi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:31.26,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, he's the \NGalaxy Sword Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.53,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.24,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how much money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.66,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we poured into making that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:41.64,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to rely on a native \Nmonkey to carry out this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.89,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he die before \Nhe could be of any use?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.86,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you spend on it, junk is—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:46.86,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.22,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that filthy mouth of yours shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.71,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:54.16,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,And he's not a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:57.41,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, he's finally made it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.85,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai is back in the \Ncountry of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:05.49,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,No more will you toy with \Nhuman lives and emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.53,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,We will make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.52,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Apprehend them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:11.67,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.47,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you, monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.60,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,That was an excellent strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:22.68,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-bo, you've come a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.69,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.17,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.68,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And that hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You always gave in to my persistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.69,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and let me win once while \Nsaying that I'd gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.87,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You were always joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.26,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I was serious this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.38,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Your voices pierced through \Nthis cold metal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.11,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.63,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Otae-chan's voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.46,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor Sakata's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:01.51,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Your voices summoned my soul \Nfrom this lump of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:08.40,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I was able to beat \Nmy other half at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.48,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't match up to the rest of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.90,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,but for a moment, I think I \Nknew what true strength was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:20.91,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally come home \Nwithout feeling ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:25.17,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, thank you very hamnida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.41,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't leave, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.92,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.80,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,We can all play with beam \Nsabers together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:37.01,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do a better job of preparing \Nyour bath this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.93,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.83,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:45.50,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave Shinpachi and \Nthe boss lady alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.19,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:55.90,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I just left something up in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.53,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that we wouldn't \Nbe prepared for such an event?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:08.92,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Kenofi is disabled, the energy \Nthat's accumulated inside won't vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:14.00,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, he's an unexploded bomb \Nthat can destroy an entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:18.01,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what will happen if \Nwe give him a little stimulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.23,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:23.51,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.89,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.73,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.24,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.57,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Toshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.94,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:39.82,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.57,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,discharge the energy in Obi Hajime
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.45,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,and obliterate Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:50.01,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,So once I've picked up \Nwhat I left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.66,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.29,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:58.30,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor Sakata, look \Nafter everyone for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:23.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't forget the teachings of the \NSchool of Beam Saber again, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.73,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.16,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Obi-one-niisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:35.34,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We won't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:39.24,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,So just promise... Just promise us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.02,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.84,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.78,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.56,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot that thing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.74,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.98,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Beam cannon energy fully charged!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:01.16,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,We're locked onto Kenofi's coordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.30,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.42,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Kenofi has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.08,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,That man is pointing \Nhis beam cannon at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.92,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It means nothing! Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.39,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen up, you two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:33.68,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tears are handy for washing away \Ntroubling and sad feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:38.80,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when you grow up, you'll learn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:44.02,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that there are things so sad, they \Ncan never be washed away by tears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:49.49,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That there are painful memories \Nthat should never be washed away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:56.53,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So people who are truly strong \Nlaugh when they want to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.50,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They endure all of the pain and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.01,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while laughing with everybody else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.01,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can cry all you want right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:15.52,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But one day, you must become \Nsamurai strong enough not to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.26,Kabuki,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kabuki First District
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.13,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you drop by, big guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.97,Smile,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Snack Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.57,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a bunch of cute girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.99,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.49,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.47,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,We can choose anyone we want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:56.64,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, you can choose anyone, \Nand they're all babes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.40,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Really, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.44,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take the babe named Otae.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.19,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.09,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You keep coming back every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.24,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.65,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't heard anything from Otae-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.41,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,since she went on leave a month back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.83,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,and we have no idea \Nwhen she's returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:20.13,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We're struggling right now after \Nlosing our top attraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.82,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,so could you not disrupt our business?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.63,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a month already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.26,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,That man saved our planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.54,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,but we weren't able to save anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:41.31,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Shinpachi-kun hasn't \Nbeen down to Odd Jobs since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:46.02,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,This is when they really need \Nother people by their sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:51.76,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,but the person they truly want \Nby their sides is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:56.80,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,If we go visit, we'll only \Nput more stress on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:02.42,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe I can make \Nthem smile right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:05.74,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do now is \Nwait and have faith
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.79,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,that the two of them \Nwill be able to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,their sorrow and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:16.90,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to smile and welcome \Nthem back when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.83,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.42,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,But when the time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.58,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure they'll smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.94,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.34,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's been so long since the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.19,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,were able to have some fun together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.84,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.95,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,That was long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.30,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to trouble \Neveryone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.23,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Kondo-san and Kyubei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.46,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:44.27,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The Shimura siblings \Nare back from Waiiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:47.33,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Here, we brought chocolate covered \Nmacadamia nuts as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.22,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:53.84,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we went to Planet Waiiha, \Nwhere it's always summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.75,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You know, with all these new long arcs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.52,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't had a chance to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.43,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So we decided to use the paid \Nvacation days we've accumulated
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.81,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and take some time off together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:06.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So, Planet Waiiha was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.54,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably thinking that \Nvacationing in Waiiha is too cliche.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:14.11,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a reason it's considered cliche.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.41,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ah, I understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiiha is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.79,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How am I supposed to understand?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.95,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would you choose this \Ntiming to go on vacation?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:23.08,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought that you were both \Nmoping around inside your house,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.40,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you're completely tanned!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.71,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dark as chocolate covered \Nmacadamia nuts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.51,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can't you tell, Kondo? \NThey're pushing themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.80,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This wasn't an ordinary vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.72,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They left Edo so we wouldn't \Nhave to see them suffer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:41.79,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And they're acting cheerful \Nso we don't notice that fact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.48,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't say anything that'll \Ndig the wound open again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.85,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad that you \Nenjoyed yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:52.30,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,But it must have cost \Na lot to go to Waiiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.91,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You must have had a lot saved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.49,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we paid for it with money
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we received from Obi-one-niisama's \Nlife insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:01.45,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What wound? They dug up a \Nwhole new grave on their own!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.12,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can see him! I can see \NObi-one-niisama rolling in the grave!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:06.72,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obi-one-niisama made arrangements for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.67,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}the money to be given to this \Ndojo if anything happened to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.38,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}so the money was meant \Nto be used for the dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.37,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really? So you went on vacation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.18,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.97,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You used that money to go on vacation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.76,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We were happy to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.09,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,for macadamia nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:21.97,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You used the money for macadamia nuts?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.17,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.74,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You spent the money from \Nhis life on nuts?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.10,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.50,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's gotta be mad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.48,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's going to shoot \Nbeams down from heaven!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.44,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Kyubei-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.61,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These siblings are a lot \Nstronger than I expected!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:37.55,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They've overcome their brother's death \Nand started trampling all over it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.16,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must understand, Kondo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.20,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're trying to say goodbye \Nto their memory of Obi Hajime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.92,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So they exchanged his life for \Nchocolate covered macadamia nuts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.63,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so the memories will \Nmelt like chocolate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:49.75,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that can't be it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.38,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you understand, Kondo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.15,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Macadamia nuts are really good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.47,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You just want to eat macadamia nuts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.78,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please help yourself, Kondo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:04.95,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the fruits of the legacy \Nleft behind by Obi-one-niisama's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.15,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't eat that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.32,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never eaten chocolate \Nthat was so meaningful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.36,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:14.57,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let your wishes go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We will restore this dojo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:21.11,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and make it as busy as it \Nwas when you were here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.69,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,with these macadamia nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.57,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh, I'm pretty sure \Nyou wasted the money!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.23,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would you need macadamia nuts?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.43,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:31.93,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Shin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.05,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,They're here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.79,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.47,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the dojo that's \Nlooking for students?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.03,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We've been expecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.80,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Kodokan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.75,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you'll give us \Nmacadamia nuts if we train in the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.60,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're just using the nuts as bait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.75,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi-kun! They're not \Nlooking for a home dojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.64,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,They're just plain homeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:54.91,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened to your tan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:56.17,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.82,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We can start with macadamia nuts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.57,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and hope they learn to love the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:04.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what it takes to \Nprotect the sword he loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.04,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect this samurai country...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.60,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who cares about swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.41,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the macadamia nuts already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.45,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should be looking for work \Ninstead of begging for nuts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:15.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get all the nuts you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:26.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,if you can land a clean hit on Sakata \NGintoki, substitute instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:29.21,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,for the School of Tendo \NMushin Macadamia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.37,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you get to eat your nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.39,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll all be functional \Nmembers of society again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.70,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, this is turning into \Na different kind of school!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So promise me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:48.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how difficult the training may be
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:51.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,or what kinds of hardships you face in life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,never stop smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one and only rule in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.68,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the School of Tendo Mushin Macadamia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.72,Obi,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1510,1)}Eternal Instructor\NObi Hajime
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:02.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.29,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor Obi-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.82,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.25,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Gang up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.48,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the macadamia nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.18,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.05,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:25.20,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the swords?! This \Nis turning into a kung fu dojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:29.15,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a dojo where we get beat \Nup in return for macadamia nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:32.16,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying about the \Ndetails and just smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.18,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,How can I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.80,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.05,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:53.79,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they won't help you \Nbecome decent samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.99,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.64,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.78,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.81,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,The macadamia nuts will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.24,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:11.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:11.98,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-bo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.21,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.78,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Obi-one-niisama, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:29.85,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use the money that \Nyou left for our dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:33.93,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been time for a \Nproper burial, but I promise to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.44,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,put you in a grave next to our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:39.93,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:45.36,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you can enjoy your \Nliquor and gasoline together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.16,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.71,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan and I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.94,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,and our wonderful friends
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:57.30,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,are doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:30.88,Accouncement,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:35.01,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Three years after Benizakura \NArc the New Translation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:39.39,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,we now have a completely original \Nstory by the author Sorachi Hideaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:43.91,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,which delves into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:48.97,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Gintama the Movie: The Final Act!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:50.90,Main01,Mada,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:55.57,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Watch as the Gintama \Nanime comes to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:55.95,July6,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(501,1)}In theaters July 6th
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:58.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait, what's this about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:57.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.23,0:23:58.42,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they get that idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:59.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's this Final Act business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.42,0:23:59.87,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What? The manga isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.42,0:23:59.87,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Is this just the usual \Nfooling around again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:23:59.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san and the Yaksha know nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:04.88,Ep Title,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Dog Food Doesn't \NTaste Like You Think
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:04.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Dog Food Doesn't \NTaste Like You Think
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:06.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said anything to me about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:09.84,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Gintama as usual.\NOdd Jobs as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:09.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fujita!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:10.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:14.88,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,The trio plus one animal,\N forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:12.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:14.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?!
